   BEST SELLER

Retro Matte Liquid Lipcolour

   BEST SELLER
   EXCLUSIVE FOR M·A·C LOVER MEMBERS

A lip colour that provides a splash of colour in a liquid-suede finish that
lingers.

   CA $26.00
   5 ml / 0.17 US fl oz
   View All Colours
   filter by:
   (BUTTON) All (BUTTON) berry (BUTTON) dare to wear (BUTTON) nude
   (BUTTON) orange (BUTTON) red
   (BUTTON) Best Seller (BUTTON) Limited Edition
     * Caviar
     * Burnt Spice
     * Carnivorous
     * Dance with Me
     * Fashion Legacy
     * Feels So Grand
     * Flesh Stone
     * High Drama
     * LadyBeGood
     * Quite the Standout
     * So Me
     * Topped With Brandy
     * Uniformly Fabulous
     * Young Attitude

   (BUTTON) (BUTTON)

Full Description

   For those who prefer timeless glamour to all-out flash, matte reigns
   supreme. M∙A∙C introduces a twist on this classic texture with robustly
   saturated shades of Retro Matte Liquid Lipcolour. Whichever shade you
   choose, all promise one thing: a splash of colour in a liquid-suede
   finish that is impossible to forget.

Key Claims and Benefits

     * Long-wearing, eight hours
     * Colour wears evenly and smoothly, eight hours
     * Provides stay-true colour, eight hours
     * Non-feathering, non-bleeding

Usage

     * Apply to lips using the edge of the applicator for a smooth, sharp
       shape. Use the tip of the applicator to perfect your application.
     * For a diffused look, try blending the edges of the lip with a 219
       Brush before the liquid lipcolour dries.
     * Use over Prep & Prime Lip for ultimate comfort.

Ingredients

   Ingredients: Isododecane, Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate,
   Polybutene, Petrolatum, Cyclohexasiloxane, Kaolin, Disteardimonium
   Hectorite, Beeswax\Cera Alba\Cire D'Abeille, Silica Dimethyl Silylate,
   Tocopherol, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Cyclopentasiloxane,
   Glyceryl Behenate/Eicosadioate, Tin Oxide, Propylene Carbonate,
   Caprylyl Glycol, Hexylene Glycol, Flavor (Aroma), Phenoxyethanol, [+/-
   Mica, Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891), Iron Oxides (Ci 77491), Iron Oxides
   (Ci 77492), Iron Oxides (Ci 77499), Blue 1 Lake (Ci 42090), Carmine (Ci
   75470), Red 6 (Ci 15850), Red 28 (Ci 45410), Red 30 (Ci 73360), Red 7
   Lake (Ci 15850), Red 22 Lake (Ci 45380), Red 28 Lake (Ci 45410), Red 30
   Lake (Ci 73360), Red 33 Lake (Ci 17200), Yellow 5 Lake (Ci 19140),
   Yellow 6 Lake (Ci 15985)]

   Please be aware that ingredient lists may change or vary from time to
   time. Please refer to the ingredient list on the product package you
   receive for the most up to date list of ingredients.
